React :-
 - React is a JS library used to build UI.
 - It helps to create reusable components.

JSX :-
 - JavaScript + XML.
 - It allows HTML inside JS.
 - Ex. 
    const html = <h1> Hellow students </h1>

Functional Components:-
 - Simple JS functions that writen JSX.
 -Ex.
    function welcome(){
        <h1>Hello </h1>
    }


